</pre></td></tr></tbody></table></code></pre></div></div>

<p>To use blocks in a method, you will have to look that up in the docs. This involves the <code class="highlighter-rouge">yield</code> keyword.  For example, this code will print ‚Äúhi‚Äù 3 times:</p>

